highlights.text: J Balvin has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “RITMO (Bad Boys For Life)” is the highest at #20.
“Sigues Con El” by Arcangel, Sech, and Dímelo Flow is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #104.
“Santa Claus Is Comin' to Town - Live at C.W. Post College, Greenvale, NY - December 1975” by Bruce Springsteen is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 125 spots at #72.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 155 weeks straight.
